  Locus:
    Date: 19 June 2009
    Section: 65
---
The mind expands, into the universe; the body shrinks to mouse-like size.
To be enlightened is to appreciate the dynamics of the Dharma.

When the mind soars into boundless space, the body remains confined to
earthly habitats. It is usually found scurrying around in the dark.
